&lt;li&gt;Basic Life Support (BLS) certification through the American Heart Association&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Preferred:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
