&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Position Overview&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Radiation Therapist delivers radiation therapy treatments in accordance with physician prescriptions and established clinical protocols. This entry-level role provides an opportunity to grow within a highly collaborative and mission-driven team. The ideal candidate demonstrates professionalism, accuracy, and compassion in patient interactions and treatment delivery. .&lt;strong&gt; &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
